tags.note: Under local orders red flags are flown and sentries are placed at either end of this path during live firing to ensure public safety and enable military training to take place. There is no intention to further restrict public access to this site.

tags.name: Nine Acre Wood
tags.note: Only the north edge was surveyed by GPS. The rest is a guess. It is bound by the bank on the south and track on the west side.
Confier harvested and native trees replanted 2022
